name: Mitt's GitHub Page
tagline: A hub for the things I make
body:
### About Me
I am a student that lives somewhere in the United States that enjoys coding in his free time.
I have made many things, primarily in C#; most of them aren't hosted, though.  
Of the things that are:

### Hosted Projects
* [Spell](http://github.com/Ajusa/Spell) - a game written in Javascript, in collaboration with Ajusa
* [AutoBing](http://github.com/epicmittmitt/AutoBing) - An experimental Bing Rewards bot
  * Download AutoBing's release executable [right here](https://github.com/epicmittmitt/AutoBing/releases)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
